Procedure
Procedure: To create new web pages(.html) for project and perform execution using Apache web server

Find file: goto Other location-computer-varwww>html-index.html- check content of file
2)open browsertype http://localhost/index.html
3)check output

a)To create new file:
1)	Open terminal
2)	 cd  /var/www/html
3)	 ls
4)	sudo nano hello.html
5)	type content   <h1>Hello Eveyone</h1>
6)	press Ctrl+o - Enter and Ctrl+x
7)	cat hello.html
8)	Run your WebPage:
9)	http://localhost//hello.html
10)	See the output

Allows Permissions for creating files and folders:
Change the directory ownership to current user: 1)(create folder)
$ sudo chown -R $USER:$USER /var/www//html
Now Create project folder inside html folder  (location: var/www//html)
Check it’s execution by: http://localhost/project/

2)(create files)
 touch ~/Templates/Untitled\Document
Now Create hello.html file inside html folder
